    "title": "Senior Teacher - NIT Warangal - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at NIT Warangal. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Senior Teacher to strengthen our Dhanbad-based team.\n\nAbout NIT Warangal:\nNIT Warangal is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with NIT Warangal!",
